Use the standard library
This is how to is_bored of S:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this S's length times:
      When item i in S is item 0 in "I", then:
         When i is 0, then:
            Increase count
         But, if not:
            When item (diff of i and 1) in S is item 0 in " ", then:
               Increase count
            End when
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is count
